{"tid":2005647,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"銅芯，誰跟你「同心」？ - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-05-07T08:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T08:44:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f86d2fbdaa07b17a626c3e55e8259f0607eb256d","tid":2005647,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T08:43:03.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200507/20913405/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200507%2F20913405%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdS6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=f5aaa264\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200507%2F20913405%2F&h=b35b4af5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200507/20913405/</a><br />\n<br />\n銅芯，誰跟你「同心」？ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200507/large/1588758931_221a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200507%2Flarge%2F1588758931_221a.jpg&h=5b4f6f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎爆發三個多月，香港人不理柒政府最初的禁罩令，自動自覺戴口罩保命，總算成績不俗。在香港疫情差不多受控、民間口罩供應開始充裕的情況下，柒政府突然宣佈全民派罩，一人一個可重複使用60次的「銅芯」口罩。「銅芯」？真係自作多情，誰跟你「同心」？<br />\n<br />\n香港人最需要口罩的時候，寒風凜冽，凌晨兩點鐘在連鎖店門外排隊，政府視而不見。現在，口罩基本上充裕了卻突然派，意義何在？難怪連80後美女夏蕙BB都忍不住出來抽水：「喺我最需要。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n我反而想知道，所謂重複使用是清洗後再用，還是如元秋建議般蒸煮後再用？抑或每。。。。。。。。。。嗎？<br />\n<br />\n有人踢爆這隻由創科局研發的CuMask，當中採用的「磁場抗菌」專利，被登記在「中國知識產權局」，而登記人為四個。。。。。。。。。。。專利、中國製造的口罩，希望目的只是為了香港人的健康，而不涉及利益衝突吧。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"fdedf98ed24fc97df178900a630d92e0d2ae0d63","tid":2005647,"uid":148002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T08:44:03.000Z","msg":"你又做撚嘢Post 全文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}